<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
        <div class="p-5 mb-5 border-bottom d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <span class="jpic jpic-jinja" style="font-size: 64px"></span>
          <h1 class="m-0 ms-4">Japan Pictograms on your Website</h1>
        </div>
        <p>The pictograms of <a class="link-secondary text-decoration-none" href="https://experience-japan.info/en/">Experience Japan Pictograms</a>, made easy to use for your website.<br/> Provided by <a href="https://www.yannklein.me/" class="link-secondary text-decoration-none" >Yann Klein</a>.</p>
        <h2>Summary</h2>
        <div class="list-group w-25 mb-5">
          <a href="#setup" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">1. Setup</a>
          <a href="#usage" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">2. Usage</a>
          <a href="#size" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action"> 2. a. Sizes</a>
          <a href="#pictos" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">2. b. Pictograms</a>
        </div>
        <h2 id="setup">Setup</h2>
        <p>Add this <code>link</code> to your HTML file <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>:</p>
          <pre class="border rounded p-3"><code>&ltlink rel="stylesheet" href="https://yannklein.github.io/japan-pictograms/japan-pictograms.css"&gt;</code></pre>
        <h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
        <p>Add icons following this pattern, refer to the below table for the NAME:</p>
          <pre class="border rounded p-3"><code>&ltspan class="jpic jpic-NAME"&gt&lt/span&gt;</code></pre>

        <h3 id="size" >Size and color</h3>
        <p>Japan Pictograms is a font, use normal CSS font properties to change its size, color and other font characteristics.</p>
        <table class="table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">Sample code</th>
              <th scope="col">Result</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><code>&lt;span class="jpic jpic-ise-jingu" style="font-size: 64px; color: red"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</code></span></td>
              <td><span class="jpic jpic-ise-jingu" style="font-size: 64px; color: red"></span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 id="pictos" >Pictograms</h3>
        <table class="table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">NAME</th>
              <th scope="col">Sample code</th>
              <th scope="col">Result</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% pictos.each do |picto| -%>
            <tr>
              <td><%= picto[:name] %></td>
              <td><code>&lt;span class="jpic jpic-<%= picto[:name] -%>"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</code></span></td>
              <td><span class="jpic jpic-<%= picto[:name] -%>" style="font-size: 32px;"></span></td>
            </tr>
            <% end -%>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      <p class="my-5">Find more about me on my  <a href="https://www.yannklein.me/" class="link-secondary text-decoration-none" >portfolio website</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
